{{Infobox artist | name = Paweł Kuczyński | image = | imagesize = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1976|8|12}} | birth_place = [[Szczecin, Poland]] | nationality = [[Poland|Polish]] | field = [[Graphic designer]], [[Painting|Painter]], [[Drawing|Drawer]] | alma_mater = [[University of Fine Arts in Poznań]] | movement = [[Political art]] | works = | awards = {{Interlanguage link multi|Eryk Prize|pl|3=Eryk Lipiński|vertical-align=sup}}, Special Prize of NTV Channel", Silver plate at 17th Salon of Antiwar Cartoons | website = {{URL|www.pawelkuczynski.com}} }}
'''Paweł Kuczyński''' is a Polish born political art satirist and philosopher who is anti-war. He draws and paints.
==Awards== *2013: silver plate at [[Salon of Antiwar Cartoons]] in [[Serbia]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://caricaturque.blogspot.fr/2013/09/results-of-17th-antiwar-cartoon.html|title=Results the 17th Salon of Antiwar Cartoons, Kragujevac 2013, Serbia}}</ref> *2010: Silver prize at the [[Dicaco International Cartoon Contest]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cartoonart.eu/Results/2010_ranking/cartoons/Dicaco_2010/dicaco1_2010.php|title=Results of Dicaco International Cartoon Coontest 2010 – Winners}}</ref> *''Eryk'' Award (named after [[Eryk Lipiński]]) by the [[Association of Polish Cartoonists]]<ref>[http://culture.pl/en/gallery/pawel-kuczynskis-works-image-gallery Paweł Kuczyński's Works - Image Gallery]</ref>
==Exhibitions== He held an exhibition in [[Brussels]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.muzeumkarykatury.pl/wystawy/bruksela_2011/bruksela_kuczynski_en.html|title=Paweł Kuczynski - Satirical Drawings}}</ref>
In 2015 he exhibited at Cartoon Xira soon after the [[Charlie Hebdo]] incident.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://culture.pl/en/event/the-controversial-kuczynski-at-cartoon-xira|title=The Controversial Kuczyński at Cartoon Xira}}</ref>
